## p.6 for문 비교

### 코드
```python
a_list = [number for number in range(1, 6) if number % 2 == 1]
print(a_list)

a_list = []
for number in range(1, 6):
    if number % 2 == 1:
        a_list.append(number)

print(a_list)
```

### 실행결과
```text
[1, 3, 5]
[1, 3, 5]
```

