## p.7 List Comprehension 예제

### 코드
```python
sentence = ['I', 'Love', 'Python', 'Soooooo', 'MUCH!!!']

print([word.lower() for word in sentence])
print([word for word in sentence if len(word) > 6])
print([(x, x**2, x**3) for x in range(10)])
