## p.8 두 개의 for문

### 코드
```python
rows = range(1, 4)
cols = range(1, 3)

for row in rows:
    for col in cols:
        print(row, col)

cells = [(row, col) for row in rows for col in cols]
print(cells)

for cell in cells:
    print(cell)

print([(i, j) for i in range(5) for j in range(i)])
```

### 실행결과
```text
1 1
1 2
2 1
2 2
3 1
3 2

[(1, 1), (1, 2), (2, 1), (2, 2), (3, 1), (3, 2)]

(1, 1)
(1, 2)
(2, 1)
(2, 2)
(3, 1)
(3, 2)

[(1, 0), (2, 0), (2, 1), (3, 0), (3, 1), (3, 2), (4, 0), (4, 1), (4, 2), (4, 3)]
```

